Proudly Level 1 B-BBEE, Kwatani is Africa’s leading OEM producing customized vibrating equipment. Our vibrating equipment guarantees high performance processing efficiency, continuous tonnage and cost reduction. For over 44 years, Kwatani has supplied and serviced +16 000 vibrating units across commodities in +40 countries. We optimize your continuous production with tailored service packages from fully fledged service, maintenance or  cost per ton agreements, plant audits and on-site training.   